data.description: Welcome to this charming single-story residence nestled in the desirable community of Menifee Lakes!This home features 3 bedrooms,2 bathrooms with spacious and welcoming layout.The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, new fridge, new stove, new dishwashers and seamlessly connects to the high vaulted ceiling living room and dining area with plenty of natural light.The master bedroom includes a private bath with dual sinks and a separate tiled walk-in shower. Two additional bedrooms share a nearby bathroom, providing comfortable accommodation for family or guests.Step outside to the spacious backyard where you can enjoy plenty of room for entertainment.Additional features include a two-car direct access garage for added convenience.Positioned near the golf course, the residence offers easy access to amenities such as resort-style pool, catch and release fishing lakes, walking trails, parks and more. This home is fully equipped and available for purchase with SOLAR PANELS and a brand new water heater, which allows for a hassle-free move-in experience. Conveniently located near the I-215 freeway, schools, shopping, and restaurants, this residence provides an opportunity for comfortable and relaxed living!The community offers very low taxes and low HOA for all the amazing amenities you'll get!Schedule your showing today!
